Key Match Events: Josh Inglis scored 103 off 49 balls for Australia
Australia won the match by 70 runs
Cameron Green took 2 wickets for 16 runs for Australia
Marcus Stoinis took 4 wickets for 23 runs for Australia
Miscellaneous Highlights: Australia's Josh Inglis was the Player of the Match
The match was played at Grange Cricket Club, Edinburgh
Scotland elected to bowl first and Australia scored 196/4 in 20 overs
Others: The match was part of the Australia tour of Scotland
The umpires for the match were Iain McDonald and Ryan Milne
